    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Scottish narrow streets, lanes, or alleys that are usually curving in their course and lead off of main thoroughfares in towns or cities.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
